item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_Security_Certificate
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_Security_Certificate Datatype Description This is the datatype that needs to be populated and sent to SoftLayer_Product_Order::placeOrder. This datatype contains everything required to place a secure certificate order with SoftLayer. Local administrativeContact The administrator contact associated with a SSL certificate. If the contact is not provided the technical contact will be used. If the address is not provided the organization information address will be used. Type: SoftLayer_Container_Product_Order_Attribute_Contact
